branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series CVJ3 is a valve mounted cylinder with single acting, spring return or spring extend actuation. The CVJ3 is available in a 10mm or 16mm bore with 3 mounting options.  A cylinder with the auto switch installed can also be manufactured.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Series CVJ5 is a valve mounted, double acting cylinder. The operating style can be changed to normally retracted or normally extended.  CVJ5 is available in 10mm or 16mm bores sizes with three mounting options.  Series CVJ5 is auto switch capable.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Series CVM3 is a valve mounted cylinder with single acting, spring return or spring extend actuation.   CVM3 has eight mounting options available and bore  sizes range from 20mm to 40mm.  A cylinder with the  auto switch installed can also be manufactured.  
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Series CVM5 is a double acting, single rod, valve  mounted cylinder.  Operation style can be changed  to normally retracted or normally extended.   CVM5 has eight mounting options available and bore  sizes range from 20mm to 40mm.  Built-in One-touch  fittings are also available.  A cylinder with the  auto switch installed can be manufactured.  
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Series CV3 is a valve mounted, double acting cylinder. The operation style can be changed to normally retracted or normally extended.  Built-in throttle valves are provided to enable speed adjustments in each direction.  CV3 has six mounting options available and bore sizes range from 40mm to 100mm.  The CV3 series is auto switch capable.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Series CVS1 is a double acting, single rod, valve  mounted cylinder with built-in speed controller.   Operation style can be changed to normally retracted  or normally extended.  Single, double, and 3 position solenoid valves can be installed.  There are seven  mounting options available for the CVS1 series and bore sizes range from 40mm to 100mm.  An auto switch cylinder with the switch installed can also be manufactured.
&lt;/p&gt;
